        "D": "Both are zero"
      },
      "answer": "A"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "question": "In the standard coaxial system x² + y² + 2gx + c = 0, the radical axis is the line ______.",
      "difficulty": "Medium",
      "hasDiagram": false,
      "diagram_description": "",
      "options": {
        "A": "x = 0 (y-axis)",
        "B": "y = 0 (x-axis)",
        "C": "x = c",
        "D": "y = g"
      },
      "answer": "A"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "question": "If c < 0 in x² + y² + 2gx + c = 0, the coaxial system is of ______ type.",
